T1  - The Preference Survey Module: A Validated Instrument for Measuring Risk, Time, and Social Preferences
AU  - Falk, Armin
AU  - Becker, Anke
AU  - Dohmen, Thomas
AU  - Huffman, David
AU  - Sunde, Uwe
Y1  - 2022/10/31
